snippet.title: GRAVEN - Full Release Launch Trailer (ft. Kardashev)
snippet.description:
Did you hear the Good Word? GRAVEN has just left Early Access and entered 1.0.
Buy now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1371690/GRAVEN/

Featured track: "Lucido" by @KardashevBand, from the album "Peripety". Released on Subliminal Groove Records.

Track Bandcamp link:
https://kardashev.bandcamp.com/track/lucido

Buy GRAVEN 1.0
Steam: https://3drealms.live/GRAVEN-Steam
GOG: https://3drealms.live/GRAVEN-GOG
Epic Games: https://3drealms.live/GRAVEN-EGS

Check out Kardashev's music here: https://3drealms.live/Kardashev
Join the 3D Realms Discord: https://3drealms.live/Discord

Websites:
https://3drealms.com/
http://slipgate-ironworks.com
